Package: fugi
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2019-04-22
Title: Further Utilities for Genomic Interactions
Description: Provides high-level methods for manipulating the GenomicInteractions class
    to analyze ChIA-PET/Hi-C experiments. This includs annotation of genomic features 
    with interaction information and producing various plots / statistics.
